data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome to this charming pool home nestled away on the quiet streets of Winston Park. This cute-as-a-button home has been very well maintained and features 2 beds, 1 bath, single car garage - with workspace, and a bonus room that could easily be considered a 3rd bedroom or office. The fenced-in backyard is secluded with a spacious pool, making hot summer afternoons or even cool winter nights the place to be. The pool has been recently resurfaced and includes a safety fence and covered patio. Eat in kitchen space, inside laundry and ceramic tile floors, while each bedroom has been updated with brand new carpet. Roof replaced in 2019. Close proximity to Gateway Plaza Shopping, Tampa International Airport, restaurants, I-275 and downtown St. Petersburg. Don’t hesitate to schedule your appointment!
